扎克·斯塔基 (Zak Starkey) 腿部状况严重后，Mantra Of The Cosmos 取消了 Soho 演出https://www.nme.com/news/music/mantra-of-the-cosmos-cancel-soho-gig-after-zak-starkey-suffers-serious-leg-condition-3830910?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=宇宙咒语取消苏荷演出后扎克·斯塔基遭受严重腿部状况Surej SinghWed, 22 Jan 2025 03:20:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3830910 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>医生命令斯塔基休息两周</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mantra-of-the-cosmos-cancel-soho-gig-after-zak-starkey-suffers-serious-leg-condition-3830910">《Mantra Of The Cosmos》在 Zak Starkey 腿部严重受伤后取消 Soho 演出的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zak-starkey-mantra-of-the-cosmos@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在鼓手 Zak Starkey 被曝患有严重的腿部疾病后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mantra-of-the-cosmos">Mantra Of The Cosmos 乐队</a>被迫取消了在 Soho 区的一场秘密演出。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shaun-ryder-and-zak-starkey-on-mantra-of-the-cosmos-do-you-know-what-a-supergroup-means-four-guys-having-a-wank-3480446">肖恩·莱德和扎克·斯塔基谈《宇宙咒语》：“你知道超级群体是什么意思吗？四个家伙手淫”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这个超级组合由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shaun-ryder">肖恩·莱德</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/happy-mondays">《快乐星期一》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-grape">《黑葡萄》</a> ）、鼓手扎克·斯塔基（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-who">《谁人》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/aritsts/oasis">《绿洲》</a> ）、吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andy-bell">安迪·贝尔</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">《绿洲》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ride">《骑行</a>》）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bez">贝兹</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/happy-mondays">《快乐星期一》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-grape">《黑葡萄</a>》）组成，原定在 Karma 演出。 Sanctum Soho 于周二晚上（1 月 21 日）举行，但不得不在最后一刻取消。</p><p>根据一份新闻稿，斯塔基的右腿出现血栓，医生要求他服用血液稀释剂并休息两周。这一诊断迫使他们的演出被取消，尽管苏荷区的派对仍然继续进行，有几位一线明星出席。</p><p>演出被取消的几天前，Mantra Of The Cosmos 与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel Gallagher</a>合作<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-joins-mantra-of-the-cosmos-psychedelic-new-single-domino-bones-gets-dangerous-3827005">发行了迷幻单曲《Domino Bones (Gets Dangerous)》，</a>并于 1 月 19 日在利物浦进行了两场演出。乐队目前还在制作一张专辑。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Mantras of the Cosmos Domino Bones 将于 2025 年 1 月 19 日在利物浦洞穴俱乐部现场直播" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BXCvs6K6yno?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Soho 活动上播放了他们在利物浦的表演片段，Shaun Ryder 向与会者开玩笑（其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yungblud">Yungblud</a> ）：“一旦我离开这里，我就会穿上紧身裤穿上 Zak 的腿。”</p><p> Mantra Of The Cosmos 于 2023 年推出单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/happy-mondays-oasis-ride-members-launch-new-band-mantra-of-the-cosmos-3452243">《Gorilla Guerilla》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shaun-ryder-and-zak-starkey-on-mantra-of-the-cosmos-do-you-know-what-a-supergroup-means-four-guys-having-a-wank-3480446">《X (Wot You Sayin?)》</a> ，并于当年夏天在<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2025">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>首次亮相。根据新闻稿，更多单曲计划于 2025 年推出。</p><p> Starkey <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shaun-ryder-and-zak-starkey-on-mantra-of-the-cosmos-do-you-know-what-a-supergroup-means-four-guys-having-a-wank-3480446">在 2023 年接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>透露，Mantra 一起录制了“大约 175 首”歌曲。莱德说：“我们有很多材料。如果你想要一些可以持续两分半或三分钟的歌曲（笑），那么我估计我们有大约 175 首歌曲，不是吗？</p><p> “或者我们可以播放一些<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">平克·弗洛伊德</a>风格的音乐，每个音乐持续 35 分钟。这只是取决于扎克会把它变成什么样子。这就是它的有趣之处。我有时会离开工作室，回来后我会在里面放一些东西，但扎克只是将它混合成不同的东西。他挑选了我要推出的产品，我只是想让他们脸上露出微笑并享受它。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Noel Gallagher 谈“议会天空”、人工智能绿洲、1975 年和英国脱欧" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Starkey 于 2004 年开始为 Oasis 打鼓，并在他们的最后两张专辑“Don&#39;t Believe The Truth”（2005 年）和“Dig Your Own Soul”（2008 年）中演奏。目前<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552">有传言称，他将与前成员安迪·贝尔 (Andy Bell) 一起加入新的绿洲乐队</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-more-dates-added-to-2025-tour-due-to-unprecedented-demand-3788543">2025 年大型重聚巡演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mantra-of-the-cosmos-cancel-soho-gig-after-zak-starkey-suffers-serious-leg-condition-3830910">《Mantra Of The Cosmos》在 Zak Starkey 腿部严重受伤后取消 Soho 演出的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
